#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Transactions"
msgstr "Cerca d'operacions"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the <guilabel>Search transactions</guilabel> dialog to search "
"your data for transactions based on criteria that you specify. You can "
"access the dialog by selecting the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find transaction...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, or "
"typing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Podeu fer servir el diàleg <guilabel>Cerca operacions</guilabel> per a "
"cercar les dades d'operacions segons els criteris que especifiqueu. Podreu "
"accedir al diàleg seleccionat l'element de menú <menuchoice><guimenu>Edita</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Cerca una operació...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> o "
"teclejant <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Maj;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two main tabs in this dialog. The <guilabel>Criteria</guilabel> "
"tab displays a number of subtabs for specifying the search criteria. When "
"the <guibutton>Find</guibutton> button is pressed, the search is initiated "
"and all criteria that have been entered on any of the Criteria subtabs will "
"be taken into account."
msgstr ""
"Hi ha dues pestanyes principals en aquest diàleg. La pestanya "
"<guilabel>Criteris</guilabel> mostra un nombre de subpestanyes per a "
"especificar els criteris de cerca. Quan es prem el botó <guibutton>Cerca</"
"guibutton>, s'iniciarà la cerca i es tindran en compte tots els criteris que "
"s'hagin introduït a qualsevol pestanya."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the search has completed, the results will be displayed under the "
"<guilabel>Result</guilabel> tab. Below the list of results, &kmymoney; shows "
"the number of transactions that met the search criteria. Double-clicking an "
"individual transaction in the result list will bring up the appropriate "
"ledger with that transaction selected."
msgstr ""
"Una vegada s'hagi completat la cerca, els resultats es mostraran sota la "
"pestanya <guilabel>Resultat</guilabel>. A sota de la llista de resultats, el "
"&kmymoney; mostrarà el nombre d'operacions que compleixen els criteris de la "
"cerca. En fer doble clic sobre una operació individual a la llista de "
"resultats, apareixerà el llibre major apropiat amb l'operació seleccionada."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> button resets all of the fields on all of "
"the criteria subtabs back to the defaults. This allows you to specify new "
"search criteria."
msgstr ""
"El botó <guibutton>Restaura</guibutton> restablirà tots els camps en totes "
"les subpestanyes de criteris als valors predeterminats. Això permetrà "
"especificar criteris de cerca nous."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Close</guibutton> button closes the <guilabel>Search "
"Transactions</guilabel> dialog box."
msgstr ""
"El botó <guibutton>Tanca</guibutton> tancarà el diàleg <guilabel>Cerca "
"operacions</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Criteria"
msgstr "Criteri de cerca"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several subtabs under the main Criteria tab, each of which allows "
"you to specify a different type of search criteria. Below the area for "
"specifying the criteria, &kmymoney; lists each of the different types of "
"criteria that are currently specified for the search."
msgstr ""
"Hi ha diverses subpestanyes sota de la pestanya principal Criteris, "
"cadascuna de les quals permet especificar un tipus diferent de criteris de "
"cerca. A sota de l'àrea per a especificar els criteris, el &kmymoney; llista "
"cadascun dels tipus de criteris diferents que s'especifiquen actualment per "
"a la cerca."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Text"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, text subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya de text</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, text subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya de text</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab allows you to specify text to search for. There are also a dropdown "
"field and two check boxes that control how the text is used in the search."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta pestanya permet especificar el text a cercar. També hi ha un menú "
"desplegable i dues caselles de selecció que controlen com s'utilitzarà el "
"text a la cerca."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "By default, the search will match on simple substrings. For example:"
msgstr ""
"De manera predeterminada, la cerca coincidirà amb subcadenes individuals. "
"Per exemple:"

# skip-rule: t-com_pu
#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "<quote>Best</quote> will find <quote>Best Cakes, Inc.</quote>"
msgstr "«Best» trobarà «Best Cakes, Inc.»"

# skip-rule: t-com_pu
#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "<quote>est</quote> will also find <quote>Best Cakes, Inc.</quote>"
msgstr "«est» també trobarà «Best Cakes, Inc.»"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the dropdown field next to the text field, select <guilabel>Contains</"
"guilabel> if you want to find transactions that contain the text, or select "
"<guilabel>Does not contain</guilabel> if you want to find transactions that "
"do not contain the specified text."
msgstr ""
"A la llista desplegable que hi ha al costat del camp de text, seleccioneu "
"<guilabel>Conté</guilabel> si voleu trobar operacions que continguin el "
"text, o seleccioneu <guilabel>No conté</guilabel> si voleu trobar operacions "
"que no continguin el text especificat."

# skip-rule: t-com_pu
#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Case Sensitive</guilabel> box, the search will be "
"case sensitive. For example, <quote>best</quote> would not find <quote>Best "
"Cakes, Inc.</quote> if this option is set."
msgstr ""
"Si marqueu la casella <guilabel>Distingeix majúscules i minúscules</"
"guilabel>, la cerca distingirà les majúscules i minúscules. Per exemple, si "
"s'ha establert aquesta opció, «best» no trobaria «Best Cakes, Inc.»."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Treat Text as regular expression</guilabel> box, "
"the text will be treated as a regular expression. For details on how to "
"craft a regular expression, visit the &Qt; documentation about the <ulink "
"url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregularexpression.html\">QRegularExpression "
"class</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Si marqueu la casella <guilabel>Tracta el text com una expressió regular</"
"guilabel>, el text es tractarà com una expressió regular. Per a obtenir "
"detalls sobre com crear una expressió regular, visiteu la documentació de "
"les &Qt; sobre la <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregularexpression.html"
"\">classe QRegularExpression</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account"
msgstr "Compte"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, account subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya de compte</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, account subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya de compte</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify the accounts that should be searched."
msgstr "Aquesta pestanya permet especificar els comptes que s'han de cercar."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Accounts are displayed in a tree format. Accounts that are marked for search "
"are indicated with a checkbox. If you click <guibutton>All</guibutton>, all "
"accounts are marked for searching. If you click <guibutton>None</guibutton>. "
"no accounts will be marked for searching. Individual accounts can be marked "
"or unmarked by clicking the box next to the account name using the &LMB;. A "
"complete hierarchy of accounts can be marked or unmarked by clicking the box "
"using the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Els comptes es mostren en format d'arbre. Els comptes marcats per a cercar "
"s'indiquen amb una casella de selecció. Si feu clic al botó <guibutton>Tots</"
"guibutton>, es marcaran per a la cerca tots els comptes. Si feu clic al botó "
"<guibutton>Cap</guibutton>, no es marcarà cap compte per a la cerca. Es "
"poden canviar individualment els comptes fent clic amb el &BER; al quadre "
"que hi ha al costat del nom del compte. Fent clic sobre el quadre amb el "
"&BDR; podreu canviar la selecció d'una estructura sencera de comptes."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Data"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, date subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya de data</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, date subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya de data</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab allows you to specify which dates should be searched. The date "
"refers to the post date of the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta pestanya permet especificar quines dates s'han de cercar. La data es "
"refereix a la data de situació de l'operació."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Range</quote> dropdown provides a convenient way to set the From "
"and To date controls. The From and To controls can be manipulated "
"individually. Dates can be entered manually, and clicking the down arrow at "
"the right of the field will bring up a typical calendar widget to select the "
"date. The controls will prevent you from entering non-existing dates. Date "
"values can also be changed by clicking the up and down arrows while the "
"cursor in within a particular part of a date."
msgstr ""
"El desplegable «Interval» proporciona una manera pràctica de configurar els "
"controls de dates «Des de» i «A». Els controls «Des de» i «A» es poden "
"manipular individualment. Les dates es poden introduir manualment, i fent "
"clic a la fletxa avall a la dreta del camp s'obrirà el giny de calendari "
"habitual per a seleccionar la data. Els controls impedeixen introduir dates "
"no existents. Els valors de la data també es poden canviar fent clic a les "
"fletxes cap amunt i cap avall quan està el cursor està en una part "
"particular d'una data."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amount"
msgstr "Import"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, amount subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya d'import</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, amount subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya d'import</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify what amounts should be searched for."
msgstr "Aquesta pestanya permet especificar quins imports s'han de cercar."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can search for an exact amount or for a range of amounts. If you click "
"the calculator icon, a small on-screen calculator will pop up to assist you "
"in entering a value."
msgstr ""
"Podreu cercar un import exacte o un interval d'imports. Si feu clic sobre la "
"icona de calculadora, apareixerà una petita calculadora en pantalla per a "
"ajudar-vos a introduir un valor."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Category"
msgstr "Categoria"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, category subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya de "
"categoria</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, category subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya de categoria</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify which categories should be searched."
msgstr "Aquesta pestanya permet especificar quines categories s'han de cercar."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Categories are displayed in a tree format, similar to Accounts. Categories "
"that are marked for search are indicated with a checkbox. If you click "
"<guibutton>All</guibutton>, all categories are marked for searching. If you "
"click <guibutton>Income</guibutton>, all income categories will be marked "
"and all expense categories will be unmarked. If you click "
"<guibutton>Expense</guibutton>, all income categories will be unmarked and "
"all expense categories will be marked. If you click <guibutton>None</"
"guibutton>, no categories will be marked for searching."
msgstr ""
"Les categories es mostren en format d'arbre, semblant als comptes. Les "
"categories marcades per a cercar s'indiquen amb una casella de selecció. Si "
"feu clic al botó <guibutton>Totes</guibutton>, es marcaran totes les "
"categories per a la cerca. Si feu clic a <guibutton>Ingrés</guibutton>, es "
"marcaran totes les categories d'ingressos i totes les categories de despeses "
"es desmarcaran. Si feu clic al botó <guibutton>Despesa</guibutton>, es "
"desmarcaran totes les categories d'ingressos i es marcaran totes les "
"categories de despeses."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Individual categories can be marked or unmarked by clicking the checkbox "
"next to the category name using the &LMB;. A complete hierarchy of "
"categories can be marked or unmarked by clicking the box using the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Es podrà canviar individualment les categories marcant o desmarcant fent "
"clic a la casella de selecció al costat del nom de la categoria utilitzant "
"el &BER;. Es podrà marcar o desmarcar tota una jerarquia de categories fent "
"clic amb el &BDR; sobre el quadre."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Tag</title>"
msgstr "<title>Etiqueta</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, tag subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya "
"d'etiquetes</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, tag subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya d'etiquetes</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify which tags should be searched."
msgstr "Aquesta pestanya permet especificar quines etiquetes s'han de cercar."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tags that are marked for search are indicated with a checked box. If you "
"click <guibutton>Select all</guibutton>, all tags are marked for searching. "
"If you click <guibutton>Select none</guibutton>, no tags will be marked for "
"searching. Individual tags can be marked or unmarked by clicking the "
"checkbox next to the payee name."
msgstr ""
"Les etiquetes que estan marcades per a la cerca s'indiquen amb un quadre. Si "
"feu clic al botó <guibutton>Selecciona-ho tot</guibutton>, es marcaran totes "
"les etiquetes per a la cerca. Si feu clic al botó <guibutton>No en "
"seleccionis cap</guibutton>, no es marcarà cap etiqueta per a la cerca. Es "
"poden marcar o desmarcar etiquetes individuals fent clic sobre la casella de "
"selecció que hi ha al costat del nom del beneficiari."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Select transactions without tags</guilabel> box, "
"only transactions with no tag will be selected."
msgstr ""
"Si marqueu la casella <guilabel>Selecciona les operacions sense etiquetes</"
"guilabel>, només se seleccionaran les operacions sense etiquetes."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payee"
msgstr "Beneficiari"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, payee subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya de "
"beneficiari</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, payee subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya de "
"beneficiari</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify which payees should be searched."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta pestanya permet especificar quins beneficiaris s'han de cercar."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Payees that are marked for search are indicated with a box. If you click "
"<guibutton>Select all</guibutton>, all payees are marked for searching. If "
"you click <guibutton>Select none</guibutton>, no payees will be marked for "
"searching. Individual payees can be marked or unmarked by clicking the box "
"next to the payee name."
msgstr ""
"Els beneficiaris que estan marcats per a la cerca s'indiquen amb un quadre. "
"Si feu clic al botó <guibutton>Selecciona-ho tot</guibutton>, es marcaran "
"tots els beneficiaris per a la cerca. Si feu clic al botó <guibutton>No en "
"seleccionis cap</guibutton>, no es marcarà cap beneficiari per a la cerca. "
"Es poden marcar o desmarcar beneficiaris individuals fent clic al quadre que "
"hi ha al costat del nom del beneficiari."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Select transactions without payees</guilabel> "
"box, only transactions with no payee will be selected."
msgstr ""
"Si marqueu la casella <guilabel>Selecciona les operacions sense "
"beneficiaris</guilabel>, només se seleccionaran les operacions sense "
"beneficiari."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Details"
msgstr "Detalls"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "search transactions, criteria tab, details subtab"
msgstr "Cerca d'operacions, pestanya de criteris, subpestanya de detalls"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search transactions Dialog, Details tab"
msgstr "Diàleg Cerca operacions, pestanya Detalls"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify various additional search criteria."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta pestanya permet especificar diversos criteris de cerca addicionals."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type can be one of the following:"
msgstr "El tipus pot ser un dels següents:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "All Types"
msgstr "Tots els tipus"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payments"
msgstr "Pagaments"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deposits"
msgstr "Ingressos"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transfers"
msgstr "Transferències"

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "State can be one of the following:"
msgstr "L'estat pot ser un dels següents:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "All states"
msgstr "Tots els estats"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Not reconciled"
msgstr "No conciliada"

